<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Applicants who have taken Advanced Placement courses in high school should request that the official scores be sent to the College's Admissions &amp; Records Office. Grades of 3, 4, or 5 on an Advanced Placement Examination will be granted college credit for the appropriate courses.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.msugf.edu/catalog/Admissions/CreditByExamination.html" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
